headline: Franklin Templeton Canada Announces Final December ETF Cash Distributions and Annual Reinvested Distributions
summary: Franklin Templeton Canada today announced the final December 2025 cash distributions and the annual reinvested distributions for its ETFs and ETF series of mutual funds available to Canadian investors. This is an update to the estimated December 2025 cash distributions and annual reinvested distributions previously announced on December 19, 2025.

headline: IVZ Among Top-Performing S&P 500 Asset Managers in 2025: Is It a Buy?
summary: Invesco soars 53.5% in 2025, topping S&P 500 asset managers. However, muted revenue growth and high intangibles raise buy-or-wait questions.
